    public class BinarySearchTree<E extends java.lang.Comparable<E>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements BinaryTreeInterface<E>
    Created by REA on 7/2/2017. Provides a binary search tree. The balanceTree method is provided to help maintain log n search efficiency.
